				<div class="book-name">The First Epistle of St. Paul to the Thessalonians — Epistola B. Pauli Apostoli ad Thessalonicenses Prima</div>
				<div class="act-chapter">
					<div class="prev-chapter"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20211129022144/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/NT/1_Th/ch_3">&lt; prev</a></div>|
